data.description: Welcome to a truly exceptional property in the highly sought-after Oakleigh Pointe community. This exquisite residence is a haven for those who appreciate the finer things in life and love to entertain.    Upon entering, you'll immediately be captivated by the rich, gleaming hardwood floors that grace the entire main level, creating an inviting and luxurious atmosphere. The formal living and dining rooms offer versatility, allowing you to tailor these spaces to your specific needs and preferences.    The heart of this home is the generously sized family room, featuring built-in shelving that elegantly frames the fireplace, creating a cozy and sophisticated ambiance. This room seamlessly flows into the outdoor oasis, a tranquil haven that beckons you to unwind and find serenity amidst lush surroundings.    The chef's dream kitchen boasts white cabinets, an inviting island with a breakfast bar, and top-of-the-line stainless-steel appliances. Noteworthy electrical upgrades, including accent lighting, dimmers, and cabinetry lighting, enhance the beauty and functionality of this space.    Step outside to the stunning patio, where a stone fireplace and UV glass and screens allow for year-round enjoyment of this outdoor sanctuary. It's an ideal setting for hosting gatherings or simply savoring moments of solitude.    On the second level, you'll discover an oversized owner's suite, complete with a sitting area for relaxation and privacy. Additionally, one of the bedrooms features a built-in Murphy bed, providing flexibility and convenience for guests or a home office.    Oakleigh Pointe offers an array of amenities to elevate your lifestyle, including tennis courts, an Olympic-sized swimming pool, a playground, and a well-appointed workout room at the clubhouse.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. Experience the epitome of gracious living in Oakleigh Pointe – a place where your every desire for comfort and entertainment can be realized. Schedule your viewing today and envision the life you've always dreamed of in this remarkable home.
